# Reflection â€” Professional Networking (STAR)

**Situation:**  
During Term 2, I completed the Professional Networking module, which focused on building meaningful professional relationships, effective communication, and personal branding within my industry.

**Task:**  
My goal was to demonstrate an understanding of how to develop and maintain a professional network by applying appropriate etiquette and communication strategies.

**Action:**  
I engaged with the online lessons and completed the Professional Networking assessment. I studied how to attend networking events, introduce myself confidently, and connect with others through professional platforms such as LinkedIn. I also learned the importance of following up and maintaining long-term connections.

**Result:**  
I achieved full marks for the assessment, which shows my understanding of professional networking principles. This experience helped me improve my confidence when engaging with professionals and taught me how to grow and manage my own career network effectively.
